        <Summary>General purpose programming language and runtime environment</Summary>
        <Description>Erlang is a general-purpose programming language and runtime environment. Erlang has built-in support for concurrency, distribution and fault tolerance. Erlang is used in several large telecommunication systems from Ericsson.</Description>
